        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figs 9–12. Taiwanaptera species, head and thorax. 9 – T. guangxiana sp. nov., holotype female; 10 – T. montana sp. nov., paratype, female (Yunnan: Huanglianshan); 11 – T. glabra Heiss & Nagashima, 2008, topotype, female; 12 – T. cf. montana, female (Yunnan: Daweishan). Arrows indicate differences in structure. Scale bar: 0.5 mm." ;
